<text><body>
<lb n="0778b06" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0778b07" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0778b08" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1179</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0778b09" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0778026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享和元年刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】永曆元年寫東寺三密藏本，【乙】久安五年寫高山寺藏本</note>文殊師利菩薩六字呪功能法經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0778b10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0778b11" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT20p0778b1101">南無一切利益尊者文殊師利童子菩薩摩訶
<lb n="0778b12" ed="T"/>薩呪曰。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0778b1204" cb:type="dharani" rend="inline">闇婆計陀那<note place="inline">上</note>摩</p><p xml:id="pT20p0778b1211" rend="inline">於此文殊師利
<lb n="0778b13" ed="T"/>菩薩六字呪功能法。我今說。若有人每日誦
<lb n="0778b14" ed="T"/>此呪七遍。決定罪業<note n="0778027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（悉）＋得【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0778027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得【大】，悉得【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0778027"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">悉得</rdg></app>除滅。若有人能每
<lb n="0778b15" ed="T"/>日誦此呪一百八遍。其人臨命終時。現前見
<lb n="0778b16" ed="T"/>文殊師利菩薩。若有人受持此呪得成法者。
<lb n="0778b17" ed="T"/>先食菜或食乳糜。或食大麥子粥。或食大麥
<lb n="0778b18" ed="T"/><g ref="#CB00595"/>或乞食。每日平旦日午日沒三時洗浴。別
<lb n="0778b19" ed="T"/>著一具淨衣。即誦此呪六十萬遍法即成就。
<lb n="0778b20" ed="T"/>於後不割斷<note n="0778028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">漊＝縷【甲】</note><note n="0778028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">漊【大】，縷【甲】</note><app n="0778028"><lem wit="【大】">漊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縷</rdg></app>楨上。其畫匠人受八戒。<note n="0778029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不＋（得）【甲】</note><note n="0778029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不【大】，不得【甲】</note><app n="0778029"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">不得</rdg></app>
<lb n="0778b21" ed="T"/><note n="0778030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">用＋（用）【乙】</note><note n="0778030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">用【大】，用用【乙】</note><app n="0778030"><lem wit="【大】">用</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">用用</rdg></app>膠畫文殊師利菩薩。於蓮華上座說法之
<lb n="0778b22" ed="T"/>像。一切莊嚴具足。作童子形天衣褡左肩。於
<lb n="0778b23" ed="T"/><note n="0778031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">右＝左ヵ【原】</note><note n="0778031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">右【大】，左【考偽-原】</note><app n="0778031"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">右</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">左</rdg></app>應畫作聖觀自在菩薩。坐蓮華座手執拂。
<lb n="0778b24" ed="T"/><note n="0778032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">左＝右【乙】</note><note n="0778032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">左【大】，右【乙】</note><app n="0778032"><lem wit="【大】">左</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">右</rdg></app>邊應畫聖普賢菩薩。<note n="0778033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（於）＋像【甲】</note><note n="0778033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">像【大】，於像【甲】</note><app n="0778033"><lem wit="【大】">像</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">於像</rdg></app>上兩邊虛空。於
<lb n="0778b25" ed="T"/>雲中出呪仙手執花鬘作。<note n="0778034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（於）＋畫【甲】</note><note n="0778034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">畫【大】，於畫【甲】</note><app n="0778034"><lem wit="【大】">畫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">於畫</rdg></app>像下應畫持呪
<lb n="0778b26" ed="T"/>人手執香爐。<note n="0778035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">瞻＝膽【乙】</note><note n="0778035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">瞻【大】，膽【乙】</note><app n="0778035"><lem wit="【大】">瞻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">膽</rdg></app>仰文殊師利菩薩。其像四邊
<lb n="0778b27" ed="T"/>皆應作山峯。於菩薩座下。應作花池充滿蓮
<lb n="0778b28" ed="T"/>華。已後於舍利塔前面向西。安楨廣大供養
<lb n="0778b29" ed="T"/>已。用蘇燃燈。取闍提花一千八枚。取一一花
<pb n="0778c" xml:id="T20.1179.0778c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0778c01" ed="T"/>各<note n="0778036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">呪一＝器【甲】</note><note n="0778036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呪一【大】，器【甲】</note><app n="0778036"><lem wit="【大】">呪一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">器</rdg></app>遍於像面散。即有<note n="0778037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（大）＋聲【甲】</note><note n="0778037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聲【大】，大聲【甲】</note><app n="0778037"><lem wit="【大】">聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大聲</rdg></app>出聞微妙聲
<lb n="0778c02" ed="T"/>或楨動。若聞妙聲時得稱心。若楨動時一切
<lb n="0778c03" ed="T"/>諍論中得勝。一切世間言教皆通達。一切眾
<lb n="0778c04" ed="T"/>生皆愛樂。若不成此法。餘一切事業皆<note n="0778038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔不〕－【乙】</note><note n="0778038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0778038"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>得
<lb n="0778c05" ed="T"/>成就。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0778c0503" rend="inline">又法沈香長八指任麁細。於蘇合香油
<lb n="0778c06" ed="T"/>塗。於以<note n="0778039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">却＝劫【甲】</note><note n="0778039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">却【大】，劫【甲】</note><app n="0778039"><lem wit="【大】">却</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">劫</rdg></app>陀羅木炭無姻火中各呪一遍。從
<lb n="0778c07" ed="T"/>初夜至明相出時燒。即見文殊師利菩薩親
<lb n="0778c08" ed="T"/>自來。於呪師前隨所求皆與滿足。唯除婬欲。</p>
<lb n="0778c09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0778c0901">又法於楨前以檀香晝夜燒不斷。誦此呪。
<lb n="0778c10" ed="T"/>文殊師利菩薩親來。為說甚深法皆得勝解。
<lb n="0778c11" ed="T"/>永離一切病得自在。得入菩薩地。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0778c1114" rend="inline">又法以
<lb n="0778c12" ed="T"/><note n="0778040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（用）＋紫【甲】</note><note n="0778040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">紫【大】，用紫【甲】</note><app n="0778040"><lem wit="【大】">紫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">用紫</rdg></app>檀長六指<note n="0778041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">剋＝刻ヵ【原】，克【甲】</note><note n="0778041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">剋【大】，刻【考偽-原】，克【甲】</note><app n="0778041"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">剋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">刻</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">克</rdg></app>作蓮華。更研紫檀<note n="0778042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">末＝未【乙】</note><note n="0778042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">末【大】，未【乙】</note><app n="0778042"><lem wit="【大】">末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">未</rdg></app>和水。
<lb n="0778c13" ed="T"/>塗之誦百千遍。<note n="0778043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">至＋（于）【甲】</note><note n="0778043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至【大】，至于【甲】</note><app n="0778043"><lem wit="【大】">至</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">至于</rdg></app>十五日夜滿月時。於楨
<lb n="0778c14" ed="T"/>前取花葉<note n="0778044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">兩＝雨【乙】</note><note n="0778044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兩【大】，雨【乙】</note><app n="0778044"><lem wit="【大】">兩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">雨</rdg></app>手<note n="0778045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔葉花〕－ヵ【原】</note><note n="0778045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">葉花【大】，〔－〕【考偽-原】</note><app n="0778045"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">葉花</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>誦呪。至於頂上光出
<lb n="0778c15" ed="T"/>即取其花。令彼人成如二八十六歲人身相
<lb n="0778c16" ed="T"/>端嚴。金色光明過於千日。威光如天童子一
<lb n="0778c17" ed="T"/>切成就。呪仙皆恭敬壽命一劫。劫盡已後往
<lb n="0778c18" ed="T"/>生極樂世界。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0778c1806" rend="inline">又法於月<note n="0778046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蝕＝食【甲】＊</note><note n="0778046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蝕【大】＊，食【甲】＊</note><app n="0778046"><lem wit="【大】">蝕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">食</rdg></app>時。取白昌<note n="0778047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蒲＝<g ref="#CB03265"/>【甲】【乙】＊</note><note n="0778047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蒲【大】＊，<g ref="#CB03265"/>【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0778047"><lem wit="【大】">蒲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><g ref="#CB03265"/></rdg></app>根。
<lb n="0778c19" ed="T"/>以瞿妹耶<note n="0778048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">糞＝戴【甲】</note><note n="0778048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">糞【大】，戴【甲】</note><app n="0778048"><lem wit="【大】">糞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">戴</rdg></app>乳酪蘇。比五和洗昌<app type="star" corresp="#0778047"><lem wit="【大】">蒲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><g ref="#CB03265"/></rdg></app>根。洗
<lb n="0778c20" ed="T"/>已。賓鉢羅樹葉<note n="0778049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">果禮＝覆ヵ【原】，裏【甲】</note><note n="0778049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">果禮【大】，覆【考偽-原】，裏【甲】</note><app n="0778049"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">果禮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">覆</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">裏</rdg></app><note place="inline">下安四葉上著三葉</note>呪至或烟出或
<lb n="0778c21" ed="T"/>煖火焰出。若煖氣時。得眾生歡喜及一切論
<lb n="0778c22" ed="T"/>難皆勝。若烟出時。得安達底壽一萬年。若火
<lb n="0778c23" ed="T"/>焰出得昇阿迦舍。<note n="0778050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">壽＋（命）【甲】</note><note n="0778050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">壽【大】，壽命【甲】</note><app n="0778050"><lem wit="【大】">壽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">壽命</rdg></app>一大劫。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0778c2312" rend="inline">又法取黃牛
<lb n="0778c24" ed="T"/>有犢子者。攢乳酪取蘇置熟銅器中。以賓鉢
<lb n="0778c25" ed="T"/>羅七葉覆之呪之。如上烟等三事成就。即服
<pb n="0779a" xml:id="T20.1179.0779a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0779a01" ed="T"/>此蘇。或多聞或安達羅。或昇阿迦舍。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0779a0115" rend="inline">又
<lb n="0779a02" ed="T"/>法取布<note n="0779001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">央＝史【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0779001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">央【大】，史【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0779001"><lem wit="【大】">央</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">史</rdg></app>迦羅子於月<app type="star" corresp="#0778046"><lem wit="【大】">蝕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">食</rdg></app>。置<note n="0779002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">日＝口【甲】</note><note n="0779002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日【大】，口【甲】</note><app n="0779002"><lem wit="【大】">日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">口</rdg></app>中含誦此
<lb n="0779a03" ed="T"/>呪。至子動時。取三種銅作珠作孔。內子於
<lb n="0779a04" ed="T"/>珠孔中<note n="0779003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">含＝口中念【甲】</note><note n="0779003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">含【大】，口中念【甲】</note><app n="0779003"><lem wit="【大】">含</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">口中念</rdg></app>住。即安陀利出口。即見之。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0779a0415" rend="inline">又法
<lb n="0779a05" ed="T"/>取<note n="0779004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">釘＝丁ヵ【原】</note><note n="0779004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">釘【大】，丁【考偽-原】</note><app n="0779004"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">釘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">丁</rdg></app>香<note n="0779005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">口＋（中）【乙】</note><note n="0779005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">口【大】，口中【乙】</note><app n="0779005"><lem wit="【大】">口</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">口中</rdg></app><note n="0779006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">含＝中念【甲】</note><note n="0779006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">含【大】，中念【甲】</note><app n="0779006"><lem wit="【大】">含</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">中念</rdg></app>。誦此呪六十萬遍已。隨共人
<lb n="0779a06" ed="T"/>語所求皆得。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0779a0606" rend="inline">又法食乳大麥子或<g ref="#CB00595"/>。誦呪
<lb n="0779a07" ed="T"/>一百二十萬遍。得成呪仙。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0779a0711" rend="inline">又法乞食不得
<lb n="0779a08" ed="T"/>語。<note n="0779007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（誦）＋滿【甲】</note><note n="0779007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滿【大】，誦滿【甲】</note><app n="0779007"><lem wit="【大】">滿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">誦滿</rdg></app>十萬遍得安達地多。若誦呪滿一俱
<lb n="0779a09" ed="T"/>胝。即見聖者文殊師利菩薩如是說法。決定
<lb n="0779a10" ed="T"/>令得入一生補處大菩薩眾。若每常誦此呪。
<lb n="0779a11" ed="T"/>一切<note n="0779008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蒙＝義【甲】</note><note n="0779008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蒙【大】，義【甲】</note><app n="0779008"><lem wit="【大】">蒙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">義</rdg></app>利皆得成就。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0779a1109" rend="inline">又法取安悉香擣末。
<lb n="0779a12" ed="T"/>以蘇和為丸。如小棗作十萬丸。一<note n="0779009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一＋（丸）【甲】</note><note n="0779009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，一丸【甲】</note><app n="0779009"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">一丸</rdg></app>皆呪一
<lb n="0779a13" ed="T"/>遍。火中燒之至盡。<note n="0779010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＋（得）【甲】</note><note n="0779010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即【大】，即得【甲】</note><app n="0779010"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即得</rdg></app>金錢十萬枚。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0779a1314" rend="inline">又法於
<lb n="0779a14" ed="T"/>流入海大河中。以一萬蓮華各呪一遍。擲置
<lb n="0779a15" ed="T"/>河中至盡。如彼蓮華數量寶伏藏見。得其藏
<lb n="0779a16" ed="T"/>受用無盡。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0779a1605" rend="inline">又法油麻以酪蘇和。一<note n="0779011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">撮＋（一撮）【甲】</note><note n="0779011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">撮【大】，撮一撮【甲】</note><app n="0779011"><lem wit="【大】">撮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">撮一撮</rdg></app>各各
<lb n="0779a17" ed="T"/><note n="0779012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">呪＝地【甲】</note><note n="0779012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呪【大】，地【甲】</note><app n="0779012"><lem wit="【大】">呪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">地</rdg></app>一遍。置火中至十萬遍。其人得財富。能
<lb n="0779a18" ed="T"/>施與一切物。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0779a1806" rend="inline">又法取未墮地瞿妹<note n="0779013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">耶＝邪【乙】</note><note n="0779013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶【大】，邪【乙】</note><app n="0779013"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">邪</rdg></app>泥地
<lb n="0779a19" ed="T"/>作壇。以種種花散其上<note n="0779014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（於壇上）＋坐【甲】</note><note n="0779014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坐【大】，於壇上坐【甲】</note><app n="0779014"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">於壇上坐</rdg></app>。每日誦呪一千八
<lb n="0779a20" ed="T"/>遍。即讀大乘經。至滿一月即得聰慧。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0779a2015" rend="inline">又法
<lb n="0779a21" ed="T"/>取牛黃呪一千八遍塗額上。一切眾生見者
<lb n="0779a22" ed="T"/>皆歡喜。於頂上髮呪七遍結之。一切惡人不
<lb n="0779a23" ed="T"/>能損害。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0779a2304" rend="inline">又法取鷄知摩羅果一萬顆。一一
<lb n="0779a24" ed="T"/>呪一遍。置火中燒至盡。一切諸病皆得除愈。</p>
<lb n="0779a25" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>文殊師利菩薩六字呪法一<note n="0779015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此下甲本奧云永曆元年十月十四日於勸修寺西山住房書校了興然，乙本奧云久安五年二月五日奉寫了，末流真宗之本</note>卷</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
<lb n="0779a26" ed="T"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pT20p0779a2601"><note n="0779016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲本乙本俱以下無之</note>以栂尾山高山寺之本。於洛北大報恩寺
<lb n="0779a27" ed="T"/>遺教會之砌寫之。八家錄云。六字神呪經
<lb n="0779a28" ed="T"/>一卷。註云或云六字呪經。貞元。梵釋欠。註
<lb n="0779a29" ed="T"/>亦云六字呪法。題云文殊師利菩薩六字
<pb n="0779b" xml:id="T20.1179.0779b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0779b01" ed="T"/>功能法。薄草子二。引用此經。</p>
<lb n="0779b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0779b0201">時天明五乙巳年二月八日　智積輪下東
<lb n="0779b03" ed="T"/>武慈忍識　享和改元仲秋八月。請求慈
<lb n="0779b04" ed="T"/>忍師之本令寫之　當山慈心院傳燈等挍
<lb n="0779b05" ed="T"/>驗加。訓予更再訂授於工公于天下。</p>
<lb n="0779b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0779b0601">豐山長谷總持蘭若沙門快道誌</p>
<lb n="0779b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0779b0701">享和三年癸亥四月朔日一校加筆畢慈順</p></cb:div>
